title: Explore Machine Learning
description: Explore Machine Learning is a Google-sponsored program for university students to get started with Machine Learning. The curriculum offers 3 tracks of Machine Learning Content (Beginner, Intermediate, Advanced) and relies on university student facilitators to train other students on campus in a two-day hands-on workshop.
